The Entrance to the Chateau of the Posse~
It would appear that a small battle happened here.  The door looks as if
it were kicked in and those inside thrown out.  The flower garden looks
as if it had seen better days.  The building itself is rather pleasing to the
eye.  It looks like a quaint and comfortable place.  It also looks like a
nice place to hide out, or plan an ambush....
~
