#4701
The Chateau of the Posse~
In the middle of this room is roaring fire.  It is a cozy room.  The place
has been well kept up considering it was taken by force from the
previous owners.  This seems like a nice place to kick back, relax, and
reflect on the day's battles.  Before you is a large pit.  The pit looks
perfect for storing extra equipment or making donations to those in
need.  To the east lies the East Wing of the Chateau.  To the west there
is a nice outdoor garden.
~
