#4702
The Office~
This appears to be the office where all the paperwork was done for the
Chateau when it was open for business.  But It would appear that the
Posse has done some remodeling.  In one corner of the room there is a
statue of Vyme the founder of the Posse.  On the west wall there is a
painting of Roxxy the clan's first recruiter.  It would appear that most of
the important decisions are made in this room.  There is a large
conference table surrounded by chairs in the middle of the room.
~
