#4703
The Garden~
As you step outside the Chateau you are met by the wonderful smell of
beautiful flowers.  Who ever cared for this garden was a master,
because even those with the blackest of hearts could easily find peace
here.  You can hear the singing of birds and the buzzing of bees as they
gather pollen from the flowers.  This seems to be one of the few places
that the Posse has left untouched since their arrival.  You spy a set of 
stairs leading down under a rose bush.  To the north is a bunk house.
~
