#4704
The Bunk House~
It would appear that all the nice beds are in here.  Although all the
bedding has been thrown about the room,  this looks like a nice place to
sleep and heal your wounds.  There are cots, beds, and bunks all over
the room.  Some of the Posse seem to be a bit sloppy, as there are
clothes and bloody weapons strewn all over the place.  For some
strange reason there seems to be something magical about the bunk
house.  It feels as if you just heal faster in here than anywhere else.
This room just gives you a feeling of  goodness, for some that makes
you feel quite at home, but for those members of the Posse that are
more evil, this room tends to make you queasy.
~
