The West Wing~
This room appears to be an art gallery.  There are breathtaking works of
art all around you.  It also appears that this room has been recently
converted to a trophy room by someone with bad taste, as there are
cryoed corpses of  those killed by the posse all about the room.
Nothing like looking at a truly beautiful painting, and a fresh corpse to
make the day complete...  A specialty store lies to the north.
~
