#4707
Posse's Portal Room~
This room has an air of anticipation about it, as though it knew you were
about to use one of its portals to hunt an unfortunate soul.  The walls
are hewn out of solid pyrite, and the floor gleams where it has been worn
from the tread of many feet.  A short ivory pillar rises from the floor,
ebony writing inscribed upon it.  Across the room from you, the wall seems
to shimmer slightly, and seems darker than the rest of the room.
~
